summary: I’m in awe of the Taylor Swift fandom.  It is filled with humans from all over the world, people of different ages, different...
body:
I’m in awe of the Taylor Swift fandom. 

It is filled with humans from all over the world, people of different ages, different cultures, different beliefs with completely different paths in life. Yet we are all united by one person. 

How can that not make you smile.

summary: Three years ago today, I saw @taylorswift for the first time at Heinz Field. It is still to this day one of my most favorite...
body:
Three years ago today, I saw @taylorswift for the first time at Heinz Field. It is still to this day one of my most favorite memories! I’m thankful that TWO months from tomorrow I will be back at Heinz Field for the Reputation Stadium Tour! Can’t wait to see you back in your home state, @taylorswift! Nothing like performing at home ❤️ See you soon!


Oh and this time, let’s take a real Polaroid picture so I can tell you my story ☺️ love you so much, Tay!


@taylorswift @taylornation @tswiftnz @tsnoticetheseposts

summary:
2 DAYS UNTIL MANCHESTER NIGHT ONE!!!
I know I've been extremely inactive over the past few months but ya gal's has finished...
caption:
2 DAYS UNTIL MANCHESTER NIGHT ONE!!!
I know I’ve been extremely inactive over the past few months but ya gal’s has finished university!!! And what a way to celebrate it by going to a Taylor concert!
It’s mad to think that the Manchester 1989 show was before I even started university and now it’s over. Where has the time gone.
I know it’s a long shot but it’d be a dream if I met Taylor. I have no idea what I’d say to her but just hugging her would make my life. Ever since I first heard Love Story I fell in love with your music, Taylor and will continue to do so until I die. Can’t believe that was 10 years ago which is coincidentally how long I’ve known my best friend who will be coming to the show with me!

We’re sat in Block 128 row 2 seats 774-775!

Any reblogs of this would mean the world to me!
@taylorswift @taylornation
